-- MOVES-LPL Financial LLC names Cronin to head state government relations
-- By Anya George Tharakan in Bangalore
-- Wed Sep 17, 2014 01:02PM EDT
-- None



Sept 17 (Reuters) - U.S. broker-dealer LPL Financial LLC, a unit of LPL Financial Holdings Inc <LPLA.O>, appointed John Cronin as vice-president, head of state government relations.

Cronin will lead in developing and maintaining relationships with the 50 U.S. states, LPL Financial said. He joined the company in March as a supervision manager.